name: "Do Wah Diddy" Playsuit
description:
Look good, look fine, the “Do Wah Diddy” playsuit will make them loose their mind! 

The first playsuit by Lady Phuncle is named after Manfred Mann’s release of the hit song “Do Wah Diddy” and captures the fun spirited nature of the 60s with its high waisted cuffed shorts leading up to the 2 buttoned sleeveless bodice.

The cute sculpted collar is made with contrasting fabric and creates a flattering V neck. 

This playsuit is made in beautiful deep green fabric with cream collar complimented with gold buttons.

Made from super fast drying suiting fabric that needs little ironing if dried flat. 

Made to have a few inches give (can be drawn in at waist with belt)
